main event: A white luminous object was observed traveling rapidly over Luzon, Philippines on February 23, 1962.
interesting points: The object was moving at an estimated speed of 5400 mph at an altitude of 12,000 feet., The object changed direction twice during the observation., The object was described as being the same size as a Boeing-707., A prior observation of Echo was believed to be Satellite Echo 1., The sighting occurred during dark night conditions with a clear atmosphere.
